These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, cooking, traveling, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, musician, entrepreneur, videographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop, pop, folk
4 different pets are kept: dog, rat, chinchilla, mouse
1. the musician is the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
3. the fan of pop is the journalist##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the musician##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the musician is the owner of the dog##1
8. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading  | puzzles  | cooking | traveling |
| Job           | musician | journalist | videographer  | entrepreneur  |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop      | soul | hip-hop      |
| Pet           | dog          | rat     | chinchilla    | mouse     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, 7up
There 4 different types of food: pear, banana, spinach, lemon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, disco, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rugby, swimming, basketball
1. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
2. the fan of d&b is the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person eating banana##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of blues##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of disco##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
9. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | juice       | almond-milk | 7up        |
| Food          | lemon     | banana       | spinach   | pear   |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | hip-hop       | d&b     | blues    |
| Sport         | swimming | basketball | handball | rugby |

