.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, soy-milk, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, firefighter, nurse, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, zombie, satire, drama
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, hamster, chinchilla
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the firefighter##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the dancer##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | sprite | cola       | lemonade        | soy-milk        |
| Job           | firefighter   | nurse | dancer   | writer |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | zombie    | drama | satire        |
| Pet           | hamster         | goat  | chinchilla       | horse         |

