4. the designer is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of soul##1
6. the fan of trance is on the right of the coach##1
7. the designer is on the right of the nurse##1
8. the indonesian is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the pony is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | coach   | nurse  | designer | project-manager |
| Music-Genre   | pop | trance       | soul       | reggae     |
| Nationality   | canadian       | japanese    | chinese     | indonesian  |
| Pet           | snake     | pony | chinchilla     | mouse         |

