.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, pilot, electrician, fisherman
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, mystery, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, chinese, japanese, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, skateboarding, baseball, parkour
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the mechanic##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
4. the chinese is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is the japanese##1
7. the spanish is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
8. the pilot is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
9. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | mechanic  | electrician    | pilot | fisherman |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery      | martial-arts    | crime         | satire    |
| Nationality   | chinese   | spanish     | japanese          | dutch      |
| Sport         | skateboarding | water-polo | parkour      | baseball      |

