.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, pepper, strawberry, carrot
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, architect, manager, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, zombie, animation, horror
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, goat, turtle
 1. the person eating strawberry is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the person eating cherry is the person watching zombie movies##1
 3. the bartender is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 4. the owner of the goat is the person eating cherry##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is the social-worker##1
 6. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 7. the manager is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 9. the manager is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | cherry  | carrot | strawberry     | pepper |
| Job           | manager  | social-worker      | bartender | architect    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | animation  | martial-arts    | horror  |
| Pet           | goat   | turtle       | chinchilla       | rabbit      |

