.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, sprite, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, video-games, gardening, traveling
4 different pets are kept: snake, mouse, hamster, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, ship, jet-ski, bus
 1. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the owner of the snake is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | cola | water     | sprite    | juice |
| Hobby       | reading | gardening    | traveling | video-games |
| Pet         | mouse   | hamster  | horse        | snake    |
| Transport   | bus   | ship | subway    | jet-ski |

