3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the firefighter is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
7. the police-officer is the person driving the trike##1
8. the person driving the roller is the person drinking tea##1
9. the person driving the train is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | tea         | hot-chocolate        | iced-tea      |
| Job           | police-officer | firefighter | nurse  | teacher  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | adventure     | disaster | action     |
