4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person driving the trike is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
9. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing | traveling | writing | magic-tricks     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | electronic       | folk       | dubstep  |
| Pet           | rat    | lizard    | fish       | guinea-pig       |
