 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
10. the person eating radish is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
